7:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企轉左HKBN後，拉入房駁落switch再拆去pc同ps4既線上唔到網，一定要直接駁來自router嗰條先上到（廳度仲有一部電腦用左router既另一條lan線。求問係咪因為HKBN限兩個ip 先咁？</blockquote><br />\nprivate ip 無限嫁喎，呀哥<span style=\"color: violet;\"></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係好睇得明你點駁啲線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪 hkbn 線駁router , router 駁switch, switch 駁 其他 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRouter一條分去廳既電腦一條入我房駁switch"},{"pid":"f25dffe98c7a56b6a96117f143047905c1f0b973","tid":84501,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:16:51.000Z","msg":"你一入屋插router 先定插 switch 先"},{"pid":"39870d047f061c8171c6f85a55c1a70dc59aea7c","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你一入屋插router 先定插 switch 先</blockquote><br />\nRouter先"},{"pid":"daa9cb0922203364dc9cd09b38fdc6d8b114140e","tid":84501,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你一入屋插router 先定插 switch 先</blockquote><br />\nRouter先</blockquote><br />\n咁咪錯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46e547b91beba6fb2d3885558d8d2d8645c974c","tid":84501,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:49:50.000Z","msg":"你部所謂router 係堅係router<br />\n定只係hkbn 比你用果舊modem,唔包router 功能？"},{"pid":"e4cac5ee9896cd1bde4af4ea3870fcd99e8fa8c0","tid":84501,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:54:02.000Z","msg":"邊有網絡唔駁得switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔識set啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3424b53045775996ed62955d668aad2933cd84","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:58:18.000Z","msg":"Sorrysorry,講清楚啲，入屋駁modem,再駁router,由router出兩條線去廳電腦同房，房呢條就經switch去房電腦同ps4 。之前未轉hkbn時都唔駛set野，唔知點解宜家唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b46f2844411c0f273a9c9df303d2b7ae7202389","tid":84501,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"router 直插電腦上唔上到網？ 拎到咩ip"},{"pid":"025141848df754363dc2a73c8488fa00c90f7a25","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>router 直插電腦上唔上到網？ 拎到咩ip</blockquote><br />\n經router直插全部上到，係隊落switch顯示有link up但係話identify 唔到ip。（大概係咁既字眼，出左門確認唔到，見諒）"},{"pid":"fdffac0681aafc87da6238dd20ce0b74bb2b41cb","tid":84501,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:06:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcb87361e7c3dc7dc1e2420029100f98f2157c2a","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識搞咪撚扮型啦<br />\n76</blockquote><br />\n有幾型？純粹想方便啲唔駛打機時又要轉線，我覺得你出黎串串貢型屌我柒碌啲喎。我真心唔識先試同問，咁都要比你抽秤？"},{"pid":"6214830ef9fae6151df5f702fada18a0808ae50c","tid":84501,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:51:45.000Z","msg":"要睇返經router 上網電腦係咩ip 先"},{"pid":"fab3d892ef7933d8af12c734568784b5c6e75649","tid":84501,"uid":45333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"Modem 後隻 router 會唔會當左 switch 咁用？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單試下你駁落 router 部電腦，係唔係 192.168.x.x 就知...<br />\n<br />\n另外亦可以 router 出 switch 換另一個頭，可能咁岩你隻 router 死左一個頭......"},{"pid":"0cf1cbf04868869f2d7e1ddd35b52486eeacedeb","tid":84501,"uid":45333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Modem 後隻 router 會唔會當左 switch 咁用？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單試下你駁落 router 部電腦，係唔係 192.168.x.x 就知...<br />\n<br />\n另外亦可以 router 出 switch 換另一個頭，可能咁岩你隻 router 死左一個頭......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 又可以掉轉，睇下 modem-&gt;switch-&gt; router 拎唔拎到 IP, 可以 verify 隻 switch 是否 work<br />\n- ok 既話就睇下換返正常 router-&gt;switch 時, 試下 behind switch 下 ping 唔 ping 到 router, 唔得既試下個 switch 駁落 router 另一個頭<br />\n- 都唔得既就試下 PS 直駁 router 上唔上到....<br />\n- 再唔得既諗唔到，要睇左情形先知下一步點做。"},{"pid":"2a1e0963b1ac2ebefe18ceba6b18a98364a99961","tid":84501,"uid":67718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"同你一樣情況但冇問題<br />\n都冇特別set過野"},{"pid":"4103d0a8756246f009ca0866b9cbe4d88ef64474","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"感謝！今晚返去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77583cf64c3d3fabec5a9b75bc84ea190cc6af5","tid":84501,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"屌以為任而堂個switch"},{"pid":"d82ac3e28551520a33962fcd89048d6b6cbd0c56","tid":84501,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Modem 後隻 router 會唔會當左 switch 咁用？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單試下你駁落 router 部電腦，係唔係 192.168.x.x 就知...<br />\n<br />\n另外亦可以 router 出 switch 換另一個頭，可能咁岩你隻 router 死左一個頭......</blockquote><br />\n正常modem 插入wan port, 電腦插落LAN port就係router<br />\n樓主應該冇自己刷ddwrt倒轉wan port同lan port<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f15bb5774120b39689dae4fe1c7ba6a85ed3e2","tid":84501,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌以為任而堂個switch</blockquote><br />\n我都以後係講緊海天堂個twitch <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45afd18bec6f53ce6b37304dc57a2ccd9bba7a","tid":84501,"uid":11941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Modem 後隻 router 會唔會當左 switch 咁用？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單試下你駁落 router 部電腦，係唔係 192.168.x.x 就知...<br />\n<br />\n另外亦可以 router 出 switch 換另一個頭，可能咁岩你隻 router 死左一個頭......</blockquote><br />\n正常modem 插入wan port, 電腦插落LAN port就係router<br />\n樓主應該冇自己刷ddwrt倒轉wan port同lan port<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無喎，一向都係modem駁wan,分出黎既係駁lan"}]}